Package: TMESplit
Title: Formal Testing of Group-Specific Multicellular Coordination Programs
Version: 0.99.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kate", "Petrenko", email = "katepetrenko.y@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Detects and characterizes group-specific multicellular
    coordination programs from cell-type composition data, with formal
    statistical testing for whether coordination structure differs between
    biological groups. Implements a coupled NMF decomposition into shared and
    group-specific programs, a three-level hierarchical permutation test
    (global, per-group, per-program), and rank selection via parallel
    analysis plus reconstruction improvement. Wraps the 'TMESplitpy' Python
    implementation via 'basilisk'.
